{"title":"小巷","authors":["黄锦萍"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":1,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小巷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄锦萍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小巷不深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰好一条百米跑道——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起点线设在狭窄的巷头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终点线划在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柏油与水泥路的交接处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两排遗留的矮屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了田径单项"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永久而忠实的观众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严肃，公平的裁判，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是挺立、洒脱的电杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主妇匆匆赶路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手提负重的菜篮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被挤掉塞子的酱油瓶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已原谅了你的仓促；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然你努力快步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替代不了跑步的速度。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自行车争先追逐上班的人流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借大小不一的轮胎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲出跑道的束缚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向各自的征途。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加入小巷的喧闹——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起点线飞来“幸福”牌摩托，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抛下一串长长的雾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代化的加速，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羡慕的嫉妒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最慢的付出最多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最快的却轻松自如。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难坏了“裁判”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百米冠军该归谁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"评效率还是评辛苦？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}